### Mock Response Servisi Test İstekleri

@host = http://localhost:5000

### ============================================
### ADMIN API - Mock Yönetimi
### ============================================

### 1. Tüm mock'ları listele
GET {{host}}/_admin/mocks

### 2. Sadece aktif mock'ları listele
GET {{host}}/_admin/mocks?isActive=true

### 3. Belirli bir mock'u getir
GET {{host}}/_admin/mocks/1

### 4. Yeni mock ekle - GET request
POST {{host}}/_admin/mocks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "httpMethod": "GET",
  "route": "/api/orders",
  "statusCode": 200,
  "responseBody": "{\"orders\": [{\"id\": 1, \"total\": 250.00}, {\"id\": 2, \"total\": 180.50}]}",
  "contentType": "application/json",
  "description": "Sipariş listesi",
  "isActive": true
}

### 5. Yeni mock ekle - POST request
POST {{host}}/_admin/mocks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "httpMethod": "POST",
  "route": "/api/orders",
  "statusCode": 201,
  "responseBody": "{\"id\": 100, \"message\": \"Order created\", \"total\": 350.00}",
  "contentType": "application/json",
  "description": "Yeni sipariş oluşturma",
  "isActive": true
}

### 6. Yeni mock ekle - Parametreli route
POST {{host}}/_admin/mocks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "httpMethod": "GET",
  "route": "/api/orders/{id}",
  "statusCode": 200,
  "responseBody": "{\"id\": 1, \"status\": \"completed\", \"total\": 250.00, \"items\": [{\"name\": \"Product A\", \"price\": 250.00}]}",
  "contentType": "application/json",
  "description": "Sipariş detayı",
  "isActive": true
}

### 7. Yeni mock ekle - Query string ile
POST {{host}}/_admin/mocks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "httpMethod": "GET",
  "route": "/api/search",
  "queryString": "?q=laptop",
  "statusCode": 200,
  "responseBody": "{\"query\": \"laptop\", \"results\": [{\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Gaming Laptop\", \"price\": 1500}]}",
  "contentType": "application/json",
  "description": "Arama sonuçları",
  "isActive": true
}

### 8. Mock güncelle
PUT {{host}}/_admin/mocks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "httpMethod": "GET",
  "route": "/api/users",
  "statusCode": 200,
  "responseBody": "{\"users\": [{\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"John Updated\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"name\": \"Jane Updated\"}]}",
  "contentType": "application/json",
  "description": "Güncellenmiş kullanıcı listesi",
  "isActive": true
}

### 9. Mock'u aktif/pasif yap (toggle)
PATCH {{host}}/_admin/mocks/1/toggle

### 10. Mock sil
DELETE {{host}}/_admin/mocks/5

### 11. Tüm mock'ları temizle (DİKKAT!)
# DELETE {{host}}/_admin/mocks/clear

